<div id="Idea_3035"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3035-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3035">Virtual democracy&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/4448-4049">johnny5_13</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">7 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">A website addressing proposed policy changes allowing for public vote & comment.  Such a site should be developed & improved with the idea of becoming a binding mechanism for modifying & implementing policy.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_3035" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_3035', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2249&topicID=3035')">Comments (3)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3035"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2249">Do-It-Yourself Government</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=democracy">democracy</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=voting online">voting online</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_3035"></div>
